FT  20 FEB 93 / Stocks decrease
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MANUFACTURERS decreased their stocks of finished goods, materials and
components by a provisional, seasonally adjusted Pounds 361m in the final
quarter of last year, the Central Statistical Office said yesterday.
The decrease follows small rises in stocks in the second and third quarters
and may indicate better demand from customers.
